id: cpt_1770723786470_rqyzkq
type: web_research
title: "Deep Research: OpenClaw + MCP + LINE + Claude Agent SDK"
created: "2026-02-10T11:43:06.470Z"
updated: "2026-02-10T11:45:55.795Z"
key_insights[25]: "OpenClaw is a self-hosted AI agent framework (Node.js) with hub-and-spoke Gateway architecture on WebSocket (ws://127.0.0.1:18789)",Pi agent has minimal 4-tool core (Read/Write/Edit/Bash) with self-extension philosophy - no MCP support by design,"OpenClaw supports LINE as extension channel plugin via @openclaw/line, requires Channel Access Token + Channel Secret",OpenClaw MCP Adapter plugin (openclaw-mcp-adapter) bridges MCP servers as native agent tools,Claude Agent SDK (formerly Claude Code SDK) provides query() API for programmatic agent execution in TypeScript/Python,LINE Bot MCP Server (@line/line-bot-mcp-server) is official LINE MCP integration with 11 tools,"MCP proxy tools (mcp-proxy, mcp-bridge, mcp-remote) bridge stdio↔SSE↔HTTP transports",Streamable HTTP is the new recommended MCP transport (SSE is legacy),"OpenClaw 145K+ GitHub stars, supports 10+ messaging channels including LINE, WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord","Claude Agent SDK supports custom MCP servers via createSdkMcpServer(), subagents, hooks, sandbox, structured outputs","OpenClaw: OSS AI agent framework by Peter Steinberger, 145K+ GitHub stars, Node.js based","Gateway daemon on ws://127.0.0.1:18789 - hub-and-spoke with WebSocket+HTTP on single port","Three-layer model: Control-plane clients, Nodes (devices), WebChat","Pi Agent: minimal coding agent with only 4 tools (Read/Write/Edit/Bash), self-extension philosophy",OpenClaw does NOT natively support MCP (issue #4834 closed as not planned),Community openclaw-mcp-adapter plugin bridges MCP servers to OpenClaw agent tools,"LINE official MCP server: @line/line-bot-mcp-server with 11 tools (push/broadcast/profile/richmenu)",Claude Agent SDK (@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk) gives programmatic access to Claude Code capabilities,"SDK supports query() with MCP servers, subagents, custom tools, permission modes","4 architecture options: (1) OpenClaw hub, (2) Claude Agent SDK backend, (3) Hybrid, (4) LINE MCP + Claude Desktop","OpenClaw LINE plugin: openclaw plugins install @openclaw/line, webhook at /line/webhook","MCP transports: stdio (local), SSE (legacy remote), Streamable HTTP (recommended remote)",mcp-proxy tools available for bridging stdio<->SSE/HTTP,CVE-2026-25253 patched in v2026.1.29 (token exfiltration),"ClawHub: 700+ community skills registry with security scanning"
findings[12]: "OpenClaw Gateway binds to single port for WebSocket + HTTP, handles all channel routing",Pi agent deliberately omits MCP support - philosophy of self-extension over external dependencies,"OpenClaw LINE channel is a plugin: openclaw plugins install @openclaw/line","LINE webhook URL format: https://gateway-host/line/webhook",LINE config in ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json under channels.line namespace,Claude Agent SDK query() returns AsyncGenerator<SDKMessage> stream,"SDK supports MCP servers as stdio, SSE, HTTP, or in-process SDK types",SDK custom tools via tool() helper with Zod schemas + createSdkMcpServer(),"LINE Bot MCP Server setup: npx @line/line-bot-mcp-server with CHANNEL_ACCESS_TOKEN env",LIFF and LINE MINI App are merging into single platform in 2025-2026,CVE-2026-25253 security vulnerability patched in OpenClaw 2026.1.29,OpenClaw skills use SKILL.md format with AgentSkills standard (Anthropic origin)
refs[16]: "https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/architecture - Gateway architecture","https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels/line - LINE channel setup","https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw - Main repo (145K+ stars)","https://github.com/line/line-bot-mcp-server - Official LINE MCP Server","https://github.com/androidStern-personal/openclaw-mcp-adapter - MCP Adapter plugin","https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/agent-sdk/typescript - Claude Agent SDK TypeScript","https://github.com/anthropics/claude-agent-sdk-typescript - SDK GitHub","https://github.com/sparfenyuk/mcp-proxy - MCP proxy bridge","https://lucumr.pocoo.org/2026/1/31/pi/ - Pi agent deep dive by Armin Ronacher",docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/architecture - Gateway 3-layer architecture,github.com/openclaw/openclaw - 145K+ stars OSS project,github.com/androidStern-personal/openclaw-mcp-adapter - MCP bridge plugin,github.com/line/line-bot-mcp-server - LINE official MCP server (11 tools),platform.claude.com/docs/en/agent-sdk/typescript - Claude Agent SDK,github.com/anthropics/claude-agent-sdk-typescript - SDK source,github.com/sparfenyuk/mcp-proxy - stdio<->SSE/HTTP proxy
recommendations[7]: Use OpenClaw + LINE plugin for direct LINE↔AI agent integration,Use LINE Bot MCP Server for Claude-side LINE control via MCP,Use Claude Agent SDK for programmatic agent execution from external systems,Use mcp-proxy or mcp-remote for bridging local MCP tools to remote clients,Consider OpenClaw MCP Adapter for connecting MCP ecosystem to OpenClaw agents,Keep OpenClaw updated for security patches (CVE-2026-25253),Use Streamable HTTP over SSE for new MCP remote connections
